---
syntax: bash
---

# Application shorcuts
mod + enter      # new terminal
mod + backspace  # new browser
mod + -          # cycle through all scratchpad windows
alt + t          # bring up the floating terminal
alt + k          # bring up the keybase window
alt + s          # bring up the slack window

# Windows & focus
mod + <h,j,k,l>         # focus left,down,up,right
mod + shift + <h,j,k,l> # move focused window left,down,up,right
mod + space             # toggle focus between tiling/floating windows
mod + r                 # resize window (use h,j,k,l)
mod + shift + q         # kill window
mod + shift + f         # toggle the tiling/floating mode on a window
mod + o                 # focus on other monitor
mod + shift + o         # move the focued window to the other monitor

# Splits
mod + ;  # horizontal split
mod + v  # vertical split
mod + f  # toggle fullscreen (for the container)

# Layouts
mod + s  # stacked layout
mod + w  # tabbed layout
mod + e  # toggle split layout

# Reload configuration
mod + shift + c  # reload i3wm configuration
mod + shift + r  # restart i3wm
